Observations made during a Tour in 1816 and 1817, through that part of the Netherlands which comprises Ostend, Bruges, Ghent, Brussels, Malines, and Antwerp; With remarks on the works of art in carving, painting, and sculpture, and enquiries into the present state of agriculture, political economy, literature, the arts and laws, government and religion ...
